OL,3,CCrews tackle fire at Waitrose
OL,4,Csupermarket
OL,6,FWatch: Plumes of smoke rise from
OL,7,Fsupermarket as crews tackle blaze
OL,9,FFirefighters have been tackling a fire
OL,10,Fat a Waitrose in Sussex.
OL,12,FThey were called to the warehouse
OL,13,Fsection of the supermarket in Nevill
OL,14,FRoad, Hove just before 4am on Tuesday
OL,15,Fmorning (16 June).
OL,17,FCrews from Hove, Preston Circus and
OL,18,FEastbourne were at the scene, along
OL,19,Fwith West Sussex Fire & Rescue
OL,20,FService, police and ambulance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
