OL,3,CCrews tackle fire at Waitrose
OL,4,Csupermarket
OL,6,FThere were no reports of any
OL,7,Fcasualities.
OL,9,FPlumes of smoke could be seen rising
OL,10,Ffrom the supermarket roof as crews
OL,11,Fworked to put out the fire.
OL,13,FNevill Road was closed throughout the
OL,14,Fmorning and reopened at around 10am -
OL,15,Fwith two fire engines staying to
OL,16,Fmonitor the scene and damp down hot
OL,17,Fspots.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
