OL,3,CCrews tackle fire at Waitrose
OL,4,Csupermarket
OL,6,FA Waitrose spokesperson said: "There
OL,7,Fwas a fire in a warehouse chiller at
OL,8,Four Hove shop early this morning while
OL,9,Fthe shop was closed, which was quickly
OL,10,Fcontained thanks to the swift action
OL,11,Fof the fire service and our Partners,
OL,12,Fto whom we're incredibly grateful.
OL,14,F"The shop will reopen as soon as it's
OL,15,Fsafe to do so, and our nearby Brighton
OL,16,Fand Southwick shops remain open as
OL,17,Fusual."
